	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Oct 26th 11:31 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings all.  I am a sort of beginner here in the realm Norrath and was wondering if I could get some help.  I bought this game about 4 weeks ago and started as a ranger...that was interesting to make it short.  I'll admit rangers are fun to play and are pretty good soloers but I want a class that I know exactly what my role is.  SO I was hoping I could get some tips for playing a Cleric.  I've decided I'm going to be a Dwarf Cleric even though a halfling sounds like a good choice too.  Anyway any advice would be helpful Thanks for your time<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
